{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":68,"Text":"在那兩座樂園裡，有水果，有海棗，有石榴。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":69,"Text":"你們究竟否認你們的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":70,"Text":"在那些樂園裡，有許多賢淑佳麗的女子。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":71,"Text":"你們究竟否認你們的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":72,"Text":"她們是白皙的，是蟄居於帳幕中的。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":73,"Text":"你們究竟否認你們的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":74,"Text":"在他們的妻子之前，任何人或精靈，都未曾與她們交接過。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":75,"Text":"你們究竟否認你們的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":76,"Text":"他們靠在翠綠的坐褥和美麗的花毯上。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":77,"Text":"你們究竟否認你們的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":78,"Text":"多福哉，你具尊嚴和大德的主的名號！"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"當那件大事發生的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"沒有任何人否認其發生。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"那件大事將是能使人降級，能使人升級的；"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"當大地震盪，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"山巒粉碎，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"化為散漫的塵埃，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"而你們分為三等的時候。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"幸福者，幸福者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"薄命者，薄命者是何等的人？"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"最先行善者，是最先入樂園的人。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"這等人，確是蒙主眷顧的。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他們將在恩澤的樂園中。"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"許多前人"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"和少數後人，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"在珠寶鑲成的床榻上，"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"彼此相對地靠在上面。"}]}